                <p>Meetings at 8pm in the hall of Purley United Reformed Church, 906 Brighton Road, Purley, CR8 2LN. Tuesday 19th March Melanie Gibson-Batson Bruges - It's more than just Chocolate and Chips! (7.30pm for AGM first)</p>
                <p><%= link_to "See our programme for 2018/19", "resource/Purley_Literary_Society.pdf" %></p>
