                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="sandhist"></a>Sanderstead Local History Group. Wednesday 24th March</h3>
                <p>Want to discover more local history? If so then 'The Sanderstead Local History Group' would like to invite you to our monthly meetings held 2-4pm at All Saints Church Hall Onslow Gardens Sanderstead the last Wednesday in the month. A small charge of £2 each meeting to cover hall hire and refreshments. No annual fee. Information is on the Bourne Society website re the area covered and local history books they have produced plus details of the SLHG meetings.</p>
                  <p>2019 programme.</p>
                    <ul>
                      <li>March 27  The History of the White Bear PH, and Fickleshole farm Chelsham owned by the Alwen family by Joyce Hoad</li>
                      <li>April 24  Shirley Windmill and the Alwen family by Chris Harman</li>
                    </ul> 
                    <p>Contact Joyce Hoad [Chair] joycehoad@virginmedia.com or chris.harman@tiscali.co.uk</p>
                </td>
